Command Line Chapter Extractor for Blu-ray Disc
============================================================

## About ##

bdchapters is a basic tool to generate XML based chapter format from mpls files (Blu-Ray Disc playlist format).


### Usage ##

bdchapters -i <mpls file> -o <directory for mkv xml chapter file>
   
Given input file xxxxx.mpls, the program will output chapter xxxxx.yyyyy.xml, xxxxx.zzzzz.xml, etc.; each correspond to yyyyy.m2ts, zzzzz.m2ts, etc. that are used by xxxxx.mpls.

## Notes ##

 - requires Python 3.2+


